      <div class="msgContentFrame">Actually its pretty easy. Perhaps THE easiest weapon to skill up.  <br /> <br /> <br />Green mobs are the ones that give the highest amount of skillpoints. This doesn't mean more SP per every time you get a skillup but rather that green mobs give you a skillup almost every single time you hit them...which makes sense since greens are supposed to be even match mobs. <br /> <br /> <br />Shield, unlike other weapons, can block multiple mobs at once and you can gain sp from every single block.  <br /> <br />So you need to find a mob that hits for low damage, hits fast... that you can tank two or three of them for about 3 minutes.  <br /> <br /> <br />and that my friend, means BEES.  <br /> <br />Find a few green bee swarms, cast protect, stoneskin and regen on yourself, have cure and 2nd wind ready.... aggro the three swarms , raise that shield. <br /> <br />..and watch the Skillpoints flow in like crazy. Once you hit 10 shield they will even give you HP every time you block which makes it even EASIER to skill up this way. </div>
